-- =====================================================================
-- Plague (map 751)  --  Neltharion spawn-layer migration
-- ---------------------------------------------------------------------
-- Replaces the cata-sourced spawn layer with Project Neltharion 4.3.4's (richer
-- placement, 13 waypoint routes, pool-gating, per-spawn MovementType). Templates,
-- quests, loot, gossip stay as the cata dc-clone (id = nelt_id + 3600000). Only base-
-- visible spawns (phaseMask&1). Guid blocks: creature +13000000, gameobject +13500000, waypoint
-- +131000000, pool +131000000. Apply AFTER 01-13 (templates must exist). Idempotent.
-- =====================================================================

-- Drop ONLY the shared-template cata spawns (nelt re-adds them) + the prior Nel block.
-- The cata-only NPCs (templates nelt does not spawn) keep their cata spawns.
